name: Sebastian's Steak House Restaurant
description: Steak Restaurant in Fond du Lac, WI
overview: Casual elegance, first class food, wonderful service and a cozy atmosphere await you at Sebastian’s Steak House. Plan your wedding rehersal, birthday, anniversary, small wedding, business meeting - or any special event in your life - at Sebastian’s Steak House - the Best Steak House in Town! Our intimate banquet room seats 22. Our larger banquet room accomodates 50. Even more if you choose our popular appetizer party. Enjoy a drink, dinner or appetizer by our famous fireplace in Sebastian’s cocktail lounge with a date, friends or family.
